225
00:49:07,686 --> 00:49:10,438
Šta ne razumeš?

226
00:49:10,648 --> 00:49:12,688
Još uvek ne razumem.

227
00:49:13,776 --> 00:49:15,685
Hoćeš jednog dana.

228
00:49:24,995 --> 00:49:27,071
Ali sad  želim da razumem.

229
00:49:28,582 --> 00:49:32,282
- Onda shvati sada!
- Ali ja ne razumem.

230
00:49:32,503 --> 00:49:34,330
Shvatićeš jednom.

231
00:49:36,090 --> 00:49:37,631
Hajdemo na ručak.

232
00:49:38,676 --> 00:49:40,752
Odlazi od mene!

233
00:49:41,553 --> 00:49:44,258
Prljavi mali gade!

234
00:49:46,475 --> 00:49:48,267
Smiri se!

235
00:49:48,476 --> 00:49:52,890
Nećeš otići tek tako!
Nikako!

236
00:49:53,106 --> 00:49:55,182
Pokvaren si kao pacov!

237
00:49:57,904 --> 00:50:01,485
- Ti si skroz luda!
- Ostavi me na miru!

238
00:50:01,699 --> 00:50:05,067
Pusti me da idem!

239
